Description:  MetaVolcanoR combines differential expression results across studies, 
    for multiple differential features (proteins, genes, probes, transcripts). It implements three strategies to 
    summarize differential abundance from different studies. i) Random Effects Model 
    (REM) approach, ii) a p-value combining-approach, and iii) a vote-counting 
    approach. In all cases, MetaVolcano exploits the Volcano plot reasoning to 
    visualize the meta-analysis results.
